Small Neat Box Chef Cookbooks

for use with Scalarium.com


MongoDB originally from edelight
git://github.com/edelight/cookbooks.git

apt receipes from Opscode 
used by MongoDB to add Mongos more up to date stable releases to the installation
Ubuntu official releases of Mongo are rather out of date. 
git://github.com/opscode/cookbooks.git

hg Mercuial recipies from Napes
http://napes.co.uk/projects/chef-hg
https://bitbucket.org/niallsco/chef-cookbooks

Apache Template from Scalarium Cookbooks (apache2), which I think it based on the official Opscode receipes
git://github.com/scalarium/cookbooks.git
http://www.scalarium.com/

